  "title": "Delicious Briny Algerian Sea Bass Tagine",
  "description": "A traditional Algerian dish featuring sea bass fillets in a flavorful and aromatic tagine, perfect for a hangover cure. This recipe is Buddhist-temple-friendly and can be prepared with crumbly and briny flavors.",
